{"id":232742112,"title":"聖誕劫 快樂","content":"拖著疲憊不堪的身軀在積雪的路上，\n漫無目的，但每一步都是竭盡全力，\n傷痕累累，雪花早被染成了玫瑰色，\n這個城市，今晚活像死城，\n剩下的我，如殭屍般苟活。\n\n明明是夜，卻亮的刺眼，\n屋內與屋外的氣氛是強烈對比，\n他們都很開心，因為聖誕來臨，\n好羨慕，那些小孩的願望能在午夜實現，\n騎著馴鹿的老人從來不曾讓小孩們失望。\n\n我是被遺棄了吧，\n聖誕從來不是我的節，\n老人的名單上沒有我，\n年復一年，早習慣了，\n越想，越感到落寞，\n給自己一個機會吧。\n\n我走到那間看起來被荒廢最久的空屋，\n拿出條應景的紅色緞帶，\n用最適合今天的聖誕結，\n淒美的結束我的聖誕劫。\nhttps://i.imgur.com/tcxWlQm.jpg","excerpt":"拖著疲憊不堪的身軀在積雪的路上，漫無目的，但每一步都是竭盡全力，傷痕累累，雪花早被染成了玫瑰色，這個城市，今晚活像死城，剩下的我，如殭屍般苟活。明明是夜，卻亮的刺眼，屋內與屋外的氣氛是強烈對比，他們都","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f8acd3e6-17e9-4d9d-bc7c-bf24d94c2ad1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-23T03:17:41.205Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-23T03:17:41.205Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":2,"tags":[],"topics":["創作","隨筆","文字","聖誕節"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"詩文","forumAlias":"literature","school":"喝吻欸郎","department":"wayentingla","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":2}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/tcxWlQm.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"37a4ce28-e845-4d14-958e-f2633442698e","url":"https://i.imgur.com/tcxWlQml.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/tcxWlQml.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/tcxWlQml.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-23T03:17:41.205Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-23T03:17:41.205Z"},{"id":"37a4ce28-e845-4d14-958e-f2633442698e","url":"https://i.imgur.com/tcxWlQm.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/tcxWlQm","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/tcxWlQml.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-23T03:17:41.205Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-23T03:17:41.205Z"}],"postAvatar":""}